<HEADLINE>
<P>
WESTSIDE DIGEST: BEVERLY HILLS; 
</P>
<P>
ADULT SCHOOL REGISTRATION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Registration is open for classes in art appreciation, English as a second 
language, tax planning, printmaking and other subjects in the Beverly Hills 
Adult School's winter term. 
</P>
<P>
The classes are offered during the day and in the evening. One-day Saturday 
seminars include such topics as French pastry, astrology and "50 Romantic and 
Unusual Weddings." 
</P>
<P>
Classes begin Jan. 8. Adults may preregister at 255 S. Lasky Drive from 8 a.m. 
to noon and 1 p.m. to 4:30 p.m., Monday through Friday. Call (213) 277-4747 for 
more information. 
</P>
</TEXT>
