CASUALTIES; VIOLENCE; COMMUNIST PARTY (ROMANIA); DEMONSTRATIONS -- ROMANIA; 
POLICE BRUTALITY; MURDERS -- ROMANIA; SECURITATE (ROMANIAN SECRET SERVICE) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
