drive against Dennis Callahan of Huntington Beach. ALEXANDER GALLARDO / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, Tight squeeze -- Tustin's Robert Laubach pulls down 
rebound despite efforts of James Dingus, left, and Mustapha Abdi. C12 ALEXANDER 
GALLARDO / Los Angeles Times 
