<HEADLINE>
<P>
DESORMEAUX'S TOTAL HITS 588 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By AP 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
LAUREL, Md. 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Axspect provided record-setting jockey Kent Desormeaux with his 588th victory 
of the year and fourth of the day Wednesday in the $20,000 Ta Wee Purse at 
Laurel Race Course. 
</P>
<P>
Axspect inched away from Diane's Girl in the final yards to win by a nose in 
1:18 2/5 for 6 1/2 furlongs. 
</P>
<P>
Reyri's Song finished another half-length back in third. 
</P>
<P>
Axspect paid $5, $3.60 and $2.20 as the favorite in a field of seven fillies 
and mares. 
</P>
<P>
Diane's Girl returned $3.80 and $2.60; Reyri's Song $2.40. 
</P>
<P>
Desormeaux must average three winners per day over the final four days of the 
year to reach his goal of 600 winners in 1989. 
</P>
